@page "/"
@layout PlatformLayout

<PageTitle>Platform Control Plane</PageTitle>

<section class="platform-hero">
    <div class="platform-panel">
        <p class="platform-eyebrow">Phase 14B</p>
        <h1>Dedicated platform host is active</h1>
        <p class="platform-lead">
            The control-plane shell and the real platform administration route now live in a separate client.
            The next cleanup step is removing the old platform routes from the tenant-facing apphost.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="platform-grid">
        <article class="platform-panel">
            <h2>Platform host responsibilities</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Platform login and session entrypoints.</li>
                <li>Tenant catalog, provisioning, and lifecycle controls.</li>
                <li>Global membership management across selected tenants.</li>
            </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="platform-panel">
            <h2>Still shared underneath</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>RPC contracts and application handlers.</li>
                <li>Identity, tenancy, and other module backends.</li>
                <li>Core building blocks and module registration foundation.</li>
            </ul>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>
